# Figma Dev Mode MCP Integration Rules

## MCP Command Usage

### 1. Code Generation from Figma

```bash
# Generate React code from selected Figma frame
mcp_Figma_Dev_Mode_MCP_get_code

# Get visual reference of Figma frame
mcp_Figma_Dev_Mode_MCP_get_image

# Extract Figma design variables
mcp_Figma_Dev_Mode_MCP_get_variable_defs
```

### 2. Figma to React Conversion Rules

#### 2.1 Output Format

- **Framework**: React + TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Component Structure**: Functional components with proper typing
- **Props Interface**: Always define TypeScript interfaces

#### 2.2 Design System Compliance

- **Primary Buttons**: `#A066FF` (포인트 네온보라)
- **Secondary Buttons**: `#9A66CC` 계열 (라이트보라)
- **Danger Actions**: `#FF4D6A` (위험색)
- **Layout Wrapper**: All pages must work within `DesktopLayout` component

#### 2.3 File Organization

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── common/          # Shared components (buttons, cards, inputs)
│   ├── desk/           # Desktop-specific components
│   ├── mobile/         # Mobile-specific components
│   └── ui/             # Basic UI elements
├── layout/
│   ├── common/         # Shared layouts
│   ├── desk/           # Desktop layouts (headers, sidebars, toolbars)
│   └── mobile/         # Mobile layouts
└── pages/
    ├── desk/           # Desktop pages
    └── mobile/         # Mobile pages
```

### 3. Code Quality Standards

#### 3.1 Component Structure

```tsx
